---
title: Italian Sausages with Veggie Succotash and Tomato-ey Orzo
description: Succotash is a hearty Southern vegetable dish that traditionally contains corn and lima beans. We're switching up the beans for edamame, and tossing it up with bell peppers and zucchini!
